# TRAPPIST-1
This system is the one exposed by NASA the February 22 2017.
Information about the planets was found [on wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TRAPPIST-1).

In order to visualize it fully, set PIXEL_PER_AU to `6000` and SIMULATION_SPEED to `8e1`.


# Solar System
Includes many objects, including Tchouri and the 8 main planets.

In order to visualize simply the telluric planets, set PIXEL_PER_AU to `300` and SIMULATION_SPEED to `8e3`.
